<div class="com-share" data-id="25796" data-title="《被当成安全象征的 EMV 芯片卡要升级了》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/25796/medium/25796.jpg?1461203563" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/25796.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
